### Host Signup

This endpoint is used to sign up a new host.

#### Request Body

- `phone` (string, required): The phone number of the host.
- `password` (string, required): The password for the host account.
- `role` (string, required): The role of the host.


#### Response

The response of this request is a JSON object conforming to the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "status": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

### Verify OTP

The `Verify OTP` endpoint is used to verify the OTP (One-Time Password) sent to a phone number.

#### Request Body

- `phone` (string, required): The phone number for which the OTP was sent.
- `otp` (string, required): The OTP to be verified.


