# Update User Profile

This endpoint is used to update the profile of a user.

## Request

- Method: PUT
- URL: `{{baseUrl}}/users/profile`
- Headers: 
  - Content-Type: application/json
- Body:

| Key               | Type   | Description       |
| ----------------- | ------ | ----------------- |
| id                | string | User ID           |
| dlVerification    | string | Driving License Verification status |
| fullName          | string | Full name of the user |
| aadharVfid        | string | Aadhar Verification ID |
| Address           | string | User's address |
| currentAddressVfid| null   | Current Address Verification ID |
| mlData            | null   | Machine Learning Data (if any) |

## Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with the updated user profile information.

